These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, pilot, nurse, engineer, police-officer
House: victorian, cape-cod, colonial, gothic-revival, cottage
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, r&b, techno, gospel, punk
5 different games are played: domino, whist, bridge, snooker, scrabble
 1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is the police-officer##1
 3. the person playing whist is on the right of the victorian house##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the right of the colonial house##1
 5. the fan of r&b is the gothic-revival house##1
 6. the cape-cod house is the pilot##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 8. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
 9. the designer is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
10. the engineer is on the left of the person playing domino##1
11. the fan of r&b is the person playing domino##1
12. the fan of techno is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Job         | pilot  | designer    | engineer | nurse    | police-officer  |
| House   | cape-cod  | victorian | colonial | gothic-revival | cottage  |
| Music-Genre           | folk     | punk     | gospel  | r&b   | techno    |
| Game         | bridge | snooker    | whist | domino  | scrabble |

