.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
House: gothic-revival, colonial, townhouse, cape-cod, tower
The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, tram, helicopter, bike
5 different pets are kept: horse, frog, ferret, goat, mouse
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: weightlifting, rowing, soccer, ice-hockey, snowboarding
 1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the person who's sport is soccer is the owner of the frog##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 8. the townhouse house is the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the townhouse house##1
10. the colonial house is in the middle##1
11. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
12. the townhouse house is the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the tower house is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| House          | townhouse        | tower | colonial     | cape-cod      | gothic-revival  |
| Transport           | motorbike   | tram | bike    | helicopter | scooter |
| Pet   | ferret | goat     | mouse | horse    | frog  |
| Sport   | ice-hockey     | rowing | weightlifting    | snowboarding      | soccer    |

