 8. the mechanic is on the right of the security-guard##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is in the middle##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the teacher##1
11. the mechanic is the art-deco house##1
12. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
13. the person watching comedy movies is the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
