.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, spanish, italian, egyptian
5 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, frog, snake, hedgehog
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, blue, white, lavender, light-blue
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower, marigold, sunflower, azalea
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the spanish##1
 3. the person who likes blue is the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the person who likes ebony is the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is in the middle##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the chinese##1
10. the egyptian is the person who likes white##1
11. the indonesian is on the left of the egyptian##1
12. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Nationality          | italian        | chinese       | spanish | indonesian   | egyptian  |
| Pet   | hedgehog | frog | goldfish | ferret   | snake |
| Color   | lavender         | light-blue     | blue | ebony | white     |
| Flower     | begonia        | bellflower        | azalea    | sunflower    | marigold      |

