.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-5::.
City: liverpool, paris, new-york, rome, san-francisco
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, october, september, december, february
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, ritmeester, bongani, old-henry, pall-mall
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, bus, car, airplane
 1. the ritmeester-smoker is the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person driving the bus is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the boat##1
 7. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is in the middle##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
10. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
12. the person driving the car is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| City          | paris    | san-francisco  | new-york | liverpool    | rome      |
| Birthday           | february | september | august  | december | october |
| Cigar   | bongani           | ritmeester      | pall-mall      | old-henry        | bluemaster     |
| Transport         | helicopter         | bus  | boat   | car       | airplane  |

