The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, motorbike, jet-ski, taxi
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, bellflower, tulip, poppy, amaryllis
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 3. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who growstulip##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
12. the person who growspoppy is the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Game         | poker  | monopoly  | mah-jongg    | snooker | go |
