City: paris, hannover, rome, hamburg, venice
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, whist, bridge, go
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, green, brown, blood-red, ebony
 1. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person playing go##1
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 5. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 6. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 7. the person traveling to hannover is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
11. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
12. the person traveling to rome is the person playing bridge##1
13. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Flower      | daffodil      | rose       | begonia         | daisy  | orchid |
| City   | rome  | hamburg | hannover | paris  | venice  |
| Game   | bridge    | domino    | mah-jongg        | go | whist     |
| Color           | green | brown      | fuchsia       | blood-red   | ebony   |

