 7. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 8. the musician is on the left of the bartender##1
 9. the bartender is in the middle##1
10. the italian is on the right of the american##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the musician##1
