There are 5 different favourite colors: green, apricot, red, amber, coral
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, volleyball, cycling, snowboarding, handball
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is in the middle##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 4. the havana-smoker is the person who likes coral##1
 5. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 7. the old-henry-smoker is the person who likes apricot##1
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 9. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
11. the havana-smoker is on the far right##1
12. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1
13. the person who likes green is the person who's hobby is reading##1
14. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
